overview: S. Terry Bauknight received his Ph.D. degree in Clinical Psychology from Duke University in 1980. Dr. Bauknight is a member of the American Psychological Association, a fellow of the Maryland Psychological Association, and is listed in the National Register of Health Service Providers in Psychology. Clinical interests include anxiety and stress management, cognitive behavioral therapy, and applying attachment and social exchange theories to relationship conflicts. Dr. Terry Bauknight provides psychological services to children, adolescents, and adults in the Baltimore area.
